Basecamp Reporting Tools Suite

These tools are designed to provide aggregate summary reports for Basecamp.  

We are focusing on time reporting in this later build but will be adding additional functionality.

If you are interested in becoming a contributor on this project email Matt at matthew@emotivellc.com.


