INSTALL

1) Upload the basecamp folder to your web server.
2) Edit the config.inc and add your basecamp login details, company ID number (from Basecamp) and business rules
3) That's it just now go to the basecamp folder on your web server and look at the reports


NOTICE

Reports right now take a while to load.  There is no local caching of data so please be patient.